        "content": "<p>Do we have something similar to the <a href=\"https://hackage.haskell.org/package/base-4.21.0.0/docs/Prelude.html#t:Bounded\">Bounded Class</a> from Haskell? </p>\n<p>The context is the implementation of Bucketsort, where we would like to be able to construct the list <code>[minBound .. maxBound ]</code> from a given type <code>a</code>.</p>",
        "id": 523177050,
        "sender_full_name": "Alexandre Rademaker",
        "timestamp": 1749507270
