    {
        "content": "<p>Maybe + <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=LocallyFiniteOrder#doc\">docs#LocallyFiniteOrder</a></p>",
        "id": 523177410,
        "sender_full_name": "Jireh Loreaux",
        "timestamp": 1749507482
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Then you should be able to write <code>Finset.Icc ⊥ ⊤ : Finset α</code> for your type <code>α</code>.</p>",
